  "response": "As of my last update, Tinder limits swipes on the free version of the app to around 100 swipes per day. Once you reach this limit, you won't be able to swipe anymore until the next day, unless you upgrade to Tinder Plus, Tinder Gold, or Tinder Platinum, which offer unlimited swiping among other features. Keep in mind that app features and limits may change, so it's a good idea to check Tinder's official site or the app itself for the most up-to-date information.",
